data.description: Amazing opportunity on this spacious 4 bedroom and 3 bath Townhouse with almost 2,000 square feet of living space! This home has a nice size backyard which you can enjoy and has ground cover pavers and planter boxes! A very well kept home indeed that  features one of the bedrooms and bathroom conveniently located on the first level. The rest of the bedrooms are on the second level and the spacious master bedroom has two closets with one as a walk-in closet next to the master bath, which is equipped with ample cabinet space and dual sinks. There's also a den/loft on the second level which is currently used as study area.  All bedrooms, hallway, and stairs have been recently upgraded to beautiful  laminate floors! The fully equipped kitchen has granite counter tops and Tile floors. The kitchen connects to the laundry room and has direct access to the two car garage. The open space dining and living room has laminate floors, window shutters, and a gorgeous fireplace with a white wooden mantel. The backyard access from the dining area is perfect for gatherings with family and friends. This community has  great amenities such as a huge clubhouse, main pool, kids pool, and spa. This home is walking distance to shops, parks, and the Paseo trails. A place you can definitely call Home Sweet Home!
